Insider Activity


Individual




Robert F. Spoerry



Mr. Robert F. Spoerry is Vice Chairman at Geberit AG, Chairman at Sonova Holding AG, and Chairman at Mettler-Toledo International, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Geberit AG and Conzzeta AG.
Mr. Spoerry was previously employed as Non-Executive Director by Schaffner Holding AG and Chairman by Mettler-Toledo. He also served on the board at Holcim Ltd.
He received his graduate degree from the Swiss Federal Institute of Technology and an MBA from The University of Chicago.



